<body>
  <div class="frame">
    <aside class="side">
      <div>
        <a class="brand" href="/">
          <img src="/assets/logo/monogram.svg" alt="" />
          <div>
            <strong>Luanda Rodrigues,</strong>
            <span>Data Analyst</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <div class="intro-card">
          <p>Brazilian data analyst connecting healthcare operations, BI, machine learning and decision intelligence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="side-viz" aria-label="Abstract data visual">
          <canvas id="sideGraphCanvas"></canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="side-stats">
          <div class="stat"><strong>05</strong><span>cases</span></div>
          <div class="stat"><strong>06</strong><span>layers</span></div>
          <div class="stat"><strong>EN/PT</strong><span>site</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="links">
        <a href="mailto:luandarodrigues30@gmail.com">Email <span>↗</span></a>
        <a href="https://github.com/luandarodrigues">GitHub <span>↗</span></a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/luanda-rodrigues">LinkedIn <span>↗</span></a>
        <a href="/pt/">Portuguese <span>↗</span></a>
      </div>
    </aside>
    <main class="main">
      <nav class="topnav">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#work">Projects</a>
        <a href="#method">Cloud</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        <a class="lang" href="/pt/">PT-BR</a>
      </nav>

      <section class="hero">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow reveal">Health / Operations / Intelligence</p>
          <h1 class="reveal">Turning complex systems into <em>readable data.</em></h1>
          <div class="split reveal">
            <p>I build analytical work that connects hospital operations, public health data, SQL, BI, machine learning, graphs and decision communication.</p>
            <div class="chips">
              <span class="chip">Brazilian</span>
              <span class="chip">Remote</span>
              <span class="chip">Relocation</span>
              <span class="chip">Python</span>
              <span class="chip">SQL</span>
              <span class="chip">Power BI</span>
              <span class="chip">NetworkX</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about section" id="about">
        <div class="about-shell reveal">
          <div class="about-head">
            <div class="about-title">
              <p class="eyebrow">About / Trajectory</p>
              <h2>Engineering, healthcare and data in the same system.</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="about-text">
              <p>My path started in Biomedical Engineering and moved into Hospital Management, where I learned to read operations as systems: flows, bottlenecks, indicators, risks and decisions.</p>
              <p>At HC-UFU/EBSERH, I work close to clinical pharmacy routines, KPI monitoring and public healthcare processes. I also bring a digital layer from marketing technology, HTML email, content creation, design thinking and AI-supported workflows.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-body">
            <img class="about-photo" src="/assets/ChatGPT%20Image%2017%20de%20mai.%20de%202026%2C%2017_26_13.png" alt="Luanda Rodrigues working with a laptop" />
            <div class="about-cards">
              <article class="about-card">
                <span>01</span>
                <h3>Healthcare operations</h3>
                <p>Clinical pharmacy flows, hospital routines, public health data and service performance.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="about-card">
                <span>02</span>
                <h3>Decision intelligence</h3>
                <p>BI, KPIs, analytical models and communication shaped for practical decisions.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="about-card">
                <span>03</span>
                <h3>Technical stack</h3>
                <p>Python, SQL, Power BI, machine learning, graph analytics and NLP.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="about-card">
                <span>04</span>
                <h3>Brazilian context</h3>
                <p>Brazilian professional available for remote work and open to relocation.</p>
              </article>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="cloud-section" id="method">
        <div class="cloud-pin">
          <div class="cloud-copy">
            <p class="eyebrow">Scroll / Data Cloud</p>
            <h2>From scattered signals to decisions.</h2>
            <p>An Obsidian-style graph: smaller notes orbit larger themes. Tap to shift between dispersed exploration and analytical clusters.</p>
            <div class="actions">
              <button class="cloud-btn" id="shuffleCloud">Reshuffle graph</button>
              <button class="cloud-btn secondary" id="clusterCloud">Cluster view</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cloud-stage" id="cloudStage">
            <canvas class="graph-canvas" id="graphCanvas"></canvas>
            <div class="legend">
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="dot health"></span>Healthcare</div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="dot models"></span>Models & NLP</div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="dot ops"></span>BI & Operations</div>
            </div>
          </div>
